public abstract class AbstractGraphicComponentListModel<T extends GraphicComponent,​S extends AbstractGraphicComponentSet<T,​S>>
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel<java.lang.Object>
implements SetListener<T>
An AbstractGraphicComponentSetModel is a sorted javax.swing.ListModel containing a set of graphic components. The graphic components in this model are sorted ascendantly first by their types and then by their IDs.
